SPELL NAME  : Guardian Angel
SPELL SYNTAX: Guard <target>
SPELL COST  : 60 SP
DESCRIPTION : Through the love of Mitra, the Cleric has the power to call a
	      guardian angel for protection. The angel will try its best to 
	      resist all magical attacks on its charge. The ability to retain
	      the angel's service and the power of the angel summoned both
	      are dependent on the devotion of the Cleric.
